Process called "calculate_temporal_relevance" that takes query as MemoryQuery and memory as EpisodicMemory returns Float
Process called "calculate_contextual_match" that takes query as MemoryQuery and memory as EpisodicMemory returns Float
Process called "calculate_emotional_similarity" that takes query as MemoryQuery and memory as EpisodicMemory returns Float
Process called "calculate_retrieval_confidence" that takes memory as EpisodicMemory and relevance as Float returns Float
Process called "create_retrieval_context" that takes query as MemoryQuery and memory as EpisodicMemory returns Dictionary
Process called "take_first_n" that takes list as List[Dictionary] and n as Integer returns List[Dictionary]
